---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Privacy Policy" 
  description="Privacy Policy for Ahmad Al-Karmi's website. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your data."
>
  <section class="section pt-32 pb-16">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="font-display text-display-md text-foreground mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-foreground-muted text-sm mb-12">Last updated: January 2026</p>
        
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-foreground-secondary">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">1. Introduction</h2>
          <p>
            This Privacy Policy explains how Ahmad Al-Karmi ("I", "me", "my") collects, uses, and protects 
            your personal information when you visit ahmadkarmi.com (the "Site").
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">2. Information I Collect</h2>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-3">2.1 Information You Provide</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-4">
            <li><strong>Contact Form:</strong> Name, email address, and message content when you submit the contact form.</li>
            <li><strong>Newsletter:</strong> Email address when you subscribe to my newsletter.</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-3">2.2 Automatically Collected Information</h3>
          <p>
            I use Google Analytics 4 to understand how visitors use the Site. This may include:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-4">
            <li>Device and browser information</li>
            <li>IP address (anonymized)</li>
            <li>Pages visited and time spent</li>
            <li>Referral sources</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">3. How I Use Your Information</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-4">
            <li>To respond to your inquiries submitted via the contact form</li>
            <li>To send newsletter updates (only if you subscribed)</li>
            <li>To analyze site usage and improve the user experience</li>
            <li>To protect against spam and abuse</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">4. Cookies</h2>
          <p>
            The Site uses cookies for analytics purposes. You can accept or decline cookies when prompted. 
            If you decline, analytics data will not be collected for your session.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">5. Third-Party Services</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-4">
            <li><strong>Google Analytics:</strong> For website analytics. <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-accent hover:underline">Google Privacy Policy</a></li>
            <li><strong>Kit (ConvertKit):</strong> For newsletter management. <a href="https://kit.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-accent hover:underline">Kit Privacy Policy</a></li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">6. Data Retention</h2>
          <p>
            Contact form submissions are retained for the duration needed to respond to your inquiry. 
            Analytics data is retained according to Google Analytics' default settings (14 months).
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">7. Your Rights</h2>
          <p>You have the right to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-4">
            <li>Request access to your personal data</li>
            <li>Request correction or deletion of your data</li>
            <li>Unsubscribe from the newsletter at any time</li>
            <li>Opt out of analytics tracking via the cookie consent banner</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">8. Contact</h2>
          <p>
            For any privacy-related questions or requests, please contact me at 
            <a href="mailto:info@ahmadkarmi.com" class="text-accent hover:underline">info@ahmadkarmi.com</a>.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>
            I may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page 
            with an updated revision date.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
